PrecisAppointment of DEREK FRASER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Hellenic Republic; JACQUES NOISEUX as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the People's Democratic Republic of Algeria; BRIAN BAKER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Denmark; MICHEL PERRAULT as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Korea; and MARC-ANDRÉ BRAULT as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Namibia, with residence in Pretoria.
